query:
SELECT 
  pq.id as assignment_id,
  pq.touchpointQuestionnaireId,
  tq.questionnaireId,
  q.title as questionnaire_title,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM questions qq WHERE qq.questionnaireId = q.id) as question_count
FROM partnerQuestionnaires pq
LEFT JOIN touchpointQuestionnaires tq ON pq.touchpointQuestionnaireId = tq.id
LEFT JOIN questionnaires q ON tq.questionnaireId = q.id
WHERE pq.accessCode = 'DDSETM9RNAHB'
